Entry.JapaneseText: それにしても暗い森だねぇ……
Entry.EnglishText: Man, this forest sure is dark...
Don't you have anything else to say, <Mao>?

Entry.JapaneseText: いつどこからバイラスが襲ってくるかわからないよ。
Entry.EnglishText: You can't tell when a Birus is gonna strike.

Entry.JapaneseText: 気をつけないと、「ぱくっ！」って食べられちゃうかも。
Entry.EnglishText: If you're not careful, you're going to get CHOMPED by something.

Entry.JapaneseText: もおっ……しつこい人は嫌われるわよ！
Entry.EnglishText: Oh, I can't stand people who don't know when to knock it off!
